OL,5, A US congressman has faced a barrage of
OL,6, criticism after he posted a Christmas  
OL,7, photograph of his family posing with   
OL,8, military-style rifles, just days after 
OL,9, a deadly school shooting.              
OL,11,FKentucky's Republican representative,  
OL,12,FThomas Massie, tweeted the photo with  
OL,13,Fthe caption: "Merry Christmas! ps.     
OL,14,FSanta, please bring ammo".             
OL,16,FThe post has been condemned by a host  
OL,17,Fof families affected by gun violence,  
OL,18,Fplus figures on both sides of politics.
OL,20,FHe has been contacted for comment.     
